&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Retriever of Lost Dreams&amp;rdquo; is a puzzle game with 55 one-screen rooms. You have to collect all the Dream Stars from each one of them. But can you? It will not be an easy task.&lt;/p&gt;

